 = [[Selena Gomez]] and [[Jimmy Fallon|Jimmy]] Cry While Eating Spicy Wings (''Hot Ones'')\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|06|11}}\n| ShortSummary    = Interview performed on ''[[List of The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon episodes (2019)#ep1078|The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon]]''  \n| LineColor       = FFA6B9\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 3\n| Title           = [[Priyanka Chopra|Priyanka Chopra Jonas]] and [[Jimmy Fallon|Jimmy]] Can't Sit Still While Eating Spicy Wings w/ [[Sean Evans (interviewer)|Sean Evans]] (''Hot Ones'')\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|10|10}}\n| ShortSummary    =  Interview performed on ''[[List of The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon episodes (2019)#ep1138|The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon]]''\n| LineColor       = FFA6B9\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 4\n| Title           = [[J.J. Watt]] and [[Jimmy Fallon|Jimmy]] Get Their Feelings Hurt While Eating Spicy Wings (''Hot Ones'')\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|01|31}}\n| ShortSummary    = Interview performed on ''[[The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon]]''  \n| LineColor       = FFA6B9\n}}\n}}\n\n== Hot sauce lineup ==\nNote that in earlier seasons, the number of sauces was cut in half when there were multiple guests on the show.\n\nThe Scoville units listed below for Season 1 are based on Scott Roberts web Scoville scale whereas the following seasons are based on the units displayed in the episodes, which sometimes results in the same sauce having different ratings in different seasons.\n\n=== Season 1 lineup ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width: 35%;\"\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 5%;\"  | {{Abbr|No.|Number}}\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 70%;\" | Sauce\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width: 25%;\" | [[Scoville units]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 1\n| [[Texas Pete|Texas Pete Original Hot Sauce]]\n| 747\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2\n| [[Cholula Hot Sauce|Cholula Original Hot Sauce]]\n| 3,600\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 3\n| El Yucateco Caribbea